title: DVD Multiboot "3 en 1" version 1 2013 by Team Label.is
description:
DVD Multiboot "3 en 1" version 1 2013 - Linux Deepin,elementaryOS,Zorin OS by Team Label

This DVD iso contains 3 different Linux OS in their latest versions up to this date that can be used as live-cd or installed in your PC:

      - Linux Deepin
      - elementaryOS Luna
      - Zorin OS

You can burn it on a DVD of any kind. But please DO NOT BURN ON A USB, IT WON'T WORK.
Thanks for downloading!
